*desire to learn and acquire knowledge* -- to KNOW. This is the natural
sequence of mental evolution, the spiritual becoming transmuted into the
material or physical. The same law of descent into materiality and
re-ascent into spirituality asserted itself during the Christian era,
the reaction having stopped only just now, in our own special
*sub-race.*

That which, perhaps ten millenniums ago, was allegorized in *Pymander*
in a triune character of interpretation, meant as a record of an
astronomical, anthropological, and even alchemical fact, namely, the
