Michael, "the *generalissimos* of the fighting Celestial Host, the
*bodyguard of Jehovah*," as it would seem (see de Mirville) is also a
Titan, only with the adjective of "divine" before the cognomen. Thus
those "Uranides" who are called everywhere "divine Titans," and who,
